actions.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.
On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.
Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.
Message on House action received in Senate.

official_title: A concurrent resolution providing for a conditional recess or adjournment of the Senate from Thursday, February 4, 1993, or Friday, February 5, 1993, until Tuesday, February 16, 1993, and a conditional adjournment of the House from Thursday, February 4, 1993, or Friday, February 5, 1993, until Tuesday, February 16, 1993.

summary.text: Provides for a recess or adjournment of the Senate from February 4 or 5, 1993, until February 16, 1993, and an adjournment of the House of Representatives from February 4 or 5, 1993, until February 16, 1993.
